node.title: Late Night Recaps Democrats’ Stinging Election Results
node.alt: “Some of you may be upset by the results, but don’t panic — save your panic for climate change,” Stephen Colbert said.
node.description: Stephen Colbert said Democrats are used to being disappointed: “That’s why they’re changing their logo from the donkey to Eeyore.”
node.content: ["Welcome to Best of Late Night, a rundown of the previous night\u2019s highlights that lets you sleep \u2014 and lets us get paid to watch comedy. Here are the 50 best movies on Netflix right now.", "Republicans won elections in several key states on Tuesday, including Virginia, where Glenn Youngkin won the race for governor.", "\u201cSo, it was a disappointing night for Democrats, but Democrats are used to being disappointed,\u201d Stephen Colbert said on Wednesday night. \u201cThat\u2019s why they\u2019re changing their logo from the donkey to Eeyore.\u201d", "Samantha Bee dug into the latest on the Supreme Court\u2019s abortion rights cases during Wednesday\u2019s \u201cFull Frontal.\u201d", "Serena Williams will talk about the new film \u201cKing Richard\u201d on Thursday\u2019s \u201cJimmy Kimmel Live.\u201d", "\u201cThe Harder They Fall\u201d on Netflix is a bloody new Western about Black gunslingers, chanteuses, saloonkeepers and train robbers."]
